ActInputValue.Value:
SELECT * FROM ( SELECT "SUBSCRIBE_MESSAGE_ID", MESSAGE_NAME, SUBSTR(MESSAGE_DATA, INSTR(MESSAGE_DATA, '<Status>') + 8, INSTR(MESSAGE_DATA, '</Status>') - INSTR(MESSAGE_DATA, '<Status>') - 8) STATUS, "MESSAGE_STATUS", "ERROR_NUMBER", "ERROR_MESSAGE", "SOURCE_APP", "SOURCE_ID", "RETRY_COUNT", "CTCR_SOURCE_PROG_ID", "CTCR_SOURCE_PROG_DT", "CORRELATION_ID", "OGW_ID"
FROM JESI_WF_AMDOCS_SUBSCRIBE T WHERE SOURCE_ID IN ( SELECT SOURCE_ID FROM JESI_WF_AMDOCS_SUBSCRIBE WHERE CTCR_SOURCE_PROG_ID = '{Var Name=Order_id}' ) ORDER BY SUBSCRIBE_MESSAGE_ID DESC )

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT "SUBSCRIBE_MESSAGE_ID", MESSAGE_NAME, SUBSTR(MESSAGE_DATA, INSTR(MESSAGE_DATA, '<Status>') + 8, INSTR(MESSAGE_DATA, '</Status>') - INSTR(MESSAGE_DATA, '<Status>') - 8) STATUS, "MESSAGE_STATUS", "ERROR_NUMBER", "ERROR_MESSAGE", "SOURCE_APP", "SOURCE_ID", "RETRY_COUNT", "CTCR_SOURCE_PROG_ID", "CTCR_SOURCE_PROG_DT", "CORRELATION_ID", "OGW_ID", RANK() OVER( PARTITION BY SOURCE_ID ORDER BY CTCR_SYS_UPD_DT DESC ) CURRENT_STATUS FROM JESI_WF_AMDOCS_SUBSCRIBE T WHERE SOURCE_ID IN ( SELECT SOURCE_ID FROM JESI_WF_AMDOCS_SUBSCRIBE WHERE CTCR_SOURCE_PROG_ID = '{Var Name=Order_id}' ) ORDER BY SUBSCRIBE_MESSAGE_ID DESC ) WHERE CURRENT_STATUS = 1

select cdm_txid,cdm_entity_txid, target_system, target_main_entity_id, status,ctcr_sys_cre_dt, ctcr_source_message_name from {EnvParam App=OGW Param=Casandra}.og_cdm_entity_targets where cdm_txid='{Var Name=DSL_Barcode}' and ctcr_source_message_name='cdm/updateCDM/update_cdm_entity_target.fxml' ALLOW FILTERING
